DEPENDENCIES:

    Pod::PsuedoPod::HTML


To build the chapters:

  ./build/tools/build_chapters.pl

This will replace all L<XXX> tokens by sections/XXX.pod or examples/XXX.pl

To run the examples: ./build/tools/run.pl examples/XXX.pl


